JSON-Path
=========

Created:      2010-07-28
Home page:    <https://metacpan.org/release/JSON-Path>
Bug tracker:  <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=JSON-Path>
Maintainer:   Toby Inkster (TOBYINK) <tobyink@cpan.org>

0.205	2013-11-02

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Fix problem using JSON::Path with Devel::ptkdb.
   Fixes RT#89393.
   Henri-Damien Laurent++
   <https://rt.cpan.org/Ticket/Display.html?id=89393>

 [ Packaging ]
 - Use Dist::Inkt.

 [ Other ]
 - Use Exporter::Tiny instead of Sub::Exporter.
 - Use LV instead of lvalue.pm.

0.204	2013-02-14

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Fix `set` method which was broken in some circumstances.
   Fixes RT#83249.
   Mitsuhiro Nakamura++
   <https://rt.cpan.org/Ticket/Display.html?id=83249>

 [ Documentation ]
 - Add documentation to test suite.
 - Corrections to lvalue documentation.

0.203	2012-10-12

 [ Documentation ]
 - Minor corrections to pod.

0.202	2012-10-12

 - Added: `get` and `set` methods.
 - Added: `jpath`, `jpath1` and `jpath_map` functions.
 - Added: `map` method.
 - Added: `value` method.

0.201	2012-09-12

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Remove remaining `use Error` in test suite.

0.200	2012-09-12

 [ Packaging ]
 - Drop dependency on common::sense.
 - Modernize.

 [ Other ]
 - Updated: Switch from Error.pm exceptions to Carp::croak.

0.101	2011-09-29

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Fix retrieval of zeroth array element.

 [ Packaging ]
 - Add more test cases.

0.100	2010-08-25

 - Minor documentation improvements.
 - Updated: Support for JSON::JOM.

